{"tid":1654882,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"Dreamworks《雪人奇緣》出現支那南海九段線打J地圖","createTime":"2019-10-14T20:05:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T20:05:16.000Z","uid":285559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"097f91a4eca0d0c99508ac45e8b56f337ac481da","tid":1654882,"uid":285559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T20:05:16.000Z","msg":"Dreamworks同支那公司合作嘅大片《雪人奇緣》<br />\n入面驚現支那南海九段線打J地圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n台灣納入中國版圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日本直情唔見埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hdk6ozr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhdk6ozr.jpg&h=167b5c0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為咁 呢套奶共片已經被越南當局列為禁片<br />\n呢套片當然背後不停比支那官媒吹捧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 新华网: 作为一部向世界讲述中国故事的动画大片，《雪人奇缘》带给全球观众一段从上海到喜马拉雅雪山的奇妙旅行，让观众遍览长江、黄山、乐山大佛、喜马拉雅山等美景。影片讲述中国女孩小艺在自家楼顶意外发现了小雪人&ldquo;大毛&rdquo;, 并和小伙伴一起，经历艰辛和考验护送小雪人重返位于喜马拉雅山的家园。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2019-09/30/c_1125060621.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xinhuanet.com%2Fworld%2F2019-09%2F30%2Fc_1125060621.htm&d=ZEuQNtRgUz7rCGSUvjEm98ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=d5e44606\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2019-09/30/c_1125060621.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n環球時報: <a href=\"http://www.globaltimes.cn/content/1165266.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.globaltimes.cn%2Fcontent%2F1165266.shtml&d=ZEuQNtRgUz7rCGSUvjEm98ls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=fb1d3fbc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.globaltimes.cn/content/1165266.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n大家識做 罷睇 <br />\n同藍絲講係爛片 反問佢哋做乜唔睇《我和我的祖國》<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}